{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Provide Government grants or loans for student airline pilots",
        "additional_details": "There are no reasonable financial solutions available to student pilots to help fund their training. Currently the only options available to many people are to remortgage their house or get a loan from a bank with an exceptionally high interest rate. It is essential in order to meet the demand for new pilots in the coming years that an affordable funding solution like a student loan should be given to student pilots to allow more individuals to be able to access this career and not be in large amounts of high interest debt.",
        "background": "Student airline pilots should be given access to a Government funding solution of to cover their flight school training costs, often totalling \u00a3100,000. This could be a low-interest student loan or bursary.",
